categories: Category:Imperial Navy officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Preartes was a male lieutenant in the Galactic Empire who served aboard the cruiser-carrier Aerie. After pursuing the New Republic frigate Hellion's Dare through the Oridol Cluster but failing to prevent two of the pilots from escaping, Preartes took it as a personal failure, returning to Colonel Shakara Nuress of the 204th Imperial Fighter Wing looking to redeem himself.
